      "side": 1,
      "message": "O(N) seems fine for now. Is this list expected to remain pretty small anyways, or will we want to figure out a hash-based approach once it\u0027s ready to start polishing the backend?\n\n- follow-up after reading isCompatible() definition: since it currently is tied exactly to the number of texture samplers, that could just be the key, either into a map or an array where it\u0027s the index. Or is the compatibility check of the root signature expected to get more complicated in the future?",
      "range": {
